        "title": "Product Tour: Welcome To Meltwater",
        "description": "This article is designed to outline each step of the on-screen tour when you first log in to Meltwater.",
        "body": "<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Welcome to Meltwater!</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Watch this short video to get started. </p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-h2b-video\"><iframe src=\"https://fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/lmrh5iiojr\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Your First Search</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Let's start by setting up your first search! This tour will take you around <b>4 minutes</b> to complete. We'll use this to send you a daily digest with the news on the topics you care most about! Click the <b>Content </b>tile to get started.</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414112149/b8f683d6b20578b4eebf1b93/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Searches</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">This is where all of your saved media monitoring searches will live. </p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">To get started, click <b>View All</b>.</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414112228/28f6ed1b12440c65c3584866/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Insert your search term</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">We'll start by running a search for a topic you're interested in monitoring. Type the keyword here. (Ex. your company, product, or competitor.)</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Hit <b>Enter </b>on your keyboard to then search for your term.</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414112359/77d561e138c498ef08c7bf16/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Refine Search</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">You can refine the search topic using the fields here. You'll learn more about this in your training courses. For now, I'll show you how to set up a news digest for this topic!</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414112466/274fe39a792c4e7945b5c7a5/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>You'll Need to Save your Search</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Click <b>Save</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414112571/a423553226b5d876e2d64f3c/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Name your Search</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Give your new Search a name. This will allow you easily to find it later. Then, click <b>OK</b>.</p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414114565/b53d448f9a1befb9ae4d4122/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Now we'll set up a daily digest.</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Click Report</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414112844/de8b302cb5d8ee55cf39f506/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Next, click View All</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414112912/2738b27d0ec313636a5395b4/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Click Create Report</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">This will launch the Report Builder</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414113041/1453fe6abb6009516177ec0c/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Set up your Report</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Here is where you will set up things like your report name, recipients list, and delivery cadence. Click Next to continue.</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414113129/d6fc6ad1d8e2053a6829bc61/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Select from your list saved searches</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">For now, let's use the search we just saved.</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414113217/37b6ba8da67daf4c662a533d/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Give your report a name</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">What do you want to call this report?</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414113363/df447c16fc960eff31f7e561/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Select Recipients</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Who should receive this report?</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414113779/d5348dff636f6a1d38993416/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>Click Save</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">There are other options available for you to customize, but for now, let's go ahead and Save this report.</p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<div class=\"intercom-container intercom-align-center\"><img src=\"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/414113884/d3320ff06a40035d15a635dc/image.png\"></div>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"no-margin\"><b>All Set!</b></p>\n<p class=\"no-margin\">Voila! You're all set, nice work! If you're ready to continue with training, let me know in the chat bubble below :)</p>\n</li>\n</ol>",
